        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "80160611-5e20-43ce-84e5-f3a9a0383815",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "2025年版｜看護助手の全国平均給与・年収の実態"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "e17c6937-7b5c-4de2-b3dd-5422770b956b",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "f870610a-e050-4809-b5d4-5d6e44c1d836",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "厚生労働省の「令和5年賃金構造基本統計調査」によると、看護助手（看護補助者）の平均的な給与は以下のようになっています。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "reference-898f3c24-5305-434a-8cbd-fe47cce4e70f",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-label-70bf34e7-554e-4df3-ad31-9ae9924b5dbe",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "参考: "
          },
          {
            "_key": "reference-span-link-6a06a4ae-712b-4ca8-b5a8-82246769a211",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "link-1952d0a7-348f-4301-b64d-fc7bf724978e"
            ],
            "text": "厚生労働省 賃金構造基本統計調査"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "link-1952d0a7-348f-4301-b64d-fc7bf724978e",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/list/chinginkouzou.html"
          }
        ],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
